metadata.name: Main Street Bridge | JTB
metadata.description:
This is by far one of my favorite drone shots and one of the closest I've gotten to a bridge thus far!

So here is the story behind this one shot.

This drone shot was used in a music video I edited for an artist named NoLoveMonday for his music video "Didn't Change" (You can find it on Youtube) or my website (Truth be told, I haven't updated my website in a while so check YouTube, lol).

Get this, I was gifted the drone (mavic mini), and I had to learn how to operate the drone LITERALLY THE DAY BEFORE THE SHOOT LMAO.

Honestly, I thought it was going to be hard at first, but I was able to figure it out within hours.

Considering the fact that I had to learn this on the fly (no pun intended), I think it's actually a great shot.

Moral of the story, do what you gotta do, to get the job done.
